# ============================================================
# Docker Ignore — UniERP
# ============================================================
# For PRODUCTION builds (apps/api/Dockerfile, apps/web/Dockerfile):
#   These Dockerfiles COPY the source into the image, so we
#   exclude heavy/unnecessary directories.
#
# For DEV mode (Dockerfile.dev + docker-compose.dev.yml):
#   The monorepo is bind-mounted, so this file only affects
#   the initial COPY of scripts/docker-entrypoint.sh.
# ============================================================

# Version control
.git
.github

# IDE / Editor
.vscode
.idea
.cursor
.claude
.ai

# Build artifacts (rebuilt inside container)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Logs
**/*.log

# Local env files (container has its own env vars)
# Note: .env is loaded by docker-compose from the host, not COPY'd
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# OS files
**/Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store

# Docker files (prevent recursive context)
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile*
